headlines.description: Seth Russell threw for 376 yards and five touchdowns and also ran for a score to help fourth-ranked Baylor open the season with a 56-21 victory at SMU on Friday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: No. 4 Baylor plenty of offense in 56-21 opener at SMU

events.name: Michigan State Spartans at Western Michigan Broncos

headlines.description: Madre London ran for two touchdowns in the first several minutes of his college career to help No. 5 Michigan State build a big lead it needed to hold off Western Michigan for a 37-24 victory Fri
headlines.shortLinkText: No. 5 Michigan St. tops W. Mich 37-24, sets sights on Oregon

events.name: Washington Huskies at Boise State Broncos

headlines.description: Jeremy McNichols rushed for 89 yards and two first-half touchdowns, and No. 23 Boise State withstood a second half filled with special teams mistakes for a 16-13 victory over Washington on Friday
headlines.shortLinkText: Petersen falls short as No. 23 Broncos beat Huskies 16-13

headlines.description: Matt Johnson threw for 242 yards and a touchdown to help Charlotte beat Georgia State 23-20 in the 49ers' FBS debut Friday at the Georgia Dome.
headlines.shortLinkText: Charlotte holds off Georgia State 23-20 in FBS debut

events.name: Rhode Island Rams at Syracuse Orange

headlines.description: Eric Dungey threw for two touchdowns and Syracuse routed Rhode Island 47-0 in the opener for both teams on Friday night.

events.name: Fordham Rams at Army Black Knights

headlines.description: Chase Edmonds ran for 110 yards and three touchdowns, including a 10-yard rush to break a 29-29 tie with 12:04 left, and added 140 yards on six catches as Fordham stunned Army 37-35 in the opener
headlines.shortLinkText: Fordham knocks off another FBS team with 37-35 win over Army

events.name: Weber State Wildcats at Oregon State Beavers

headlines.description: True freshman Seth Collins threw a pair of touchdown passes, including a 44-yard fourth-quarter strike to Jordan Villamin, and Oregon State defeated Weber State 26-7 on Friday night in Gary Ander
headlines.shortLinkText: Oregon State defeats Weber State 26-7 in Andersen's debut

events.name: Kent State Golden Flashes at Illinois Fighting Illini

headlines.description: Kent State and Illinois postponed their season-opening game until Saturday after a lightning delay of almost three hours on Friday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Kent State-Illinois moved to Sat. after lightning
